The paper focuses on learning joint representations of image content and natural language, which suggests it belongs to the natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. The use of the BERT architecture and transformer layers also suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI, cs.LG). Finally, the paper also deals with image retrieval, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
